#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Bonus if > 62</guilabel>: Player is awarded an additional 35 "
"points if the summarized value of all the field above is greater than 62 "
"points."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Bonus if > 62</guilabel>: Igrač je nagrađen sa dodatnih 35 poena "
"ako sažeta vrijednost svih polja iznad je veće od 62 poena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Upper Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a "
"summary of all the fields above."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Upper Total</guilabel>: NIje polje za igranje, samo rezime svih "
"polja iznad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>3 of a Kind</guilabel>: Summarized value of dice when three of the "
"dice are bearing the same value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>3 of a Kind</guilabel>: Rezimirana vrijednost kocki kada tri kocke "
"imaju istu vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '14121'. The sum is: '9'='1'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'2'. Dice on "
"display: '55151'. The sum is: '17'='5'+'5'+'5'+'1'+'1'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '14121'. Suma je:  '9'='1'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'2'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '55151'. Suma je:  '17'='5'+'5'+'5'+'1'+'1'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>4 of a Kind</guilabel>: Summarized value of dice when four of the "
"dice are bearing the same value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>4 of a Kind</guilabel>: Rezimirana vrijednost kocke kad četiri "
"kocke imaju istu vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '41444'. The sum is: '17'='4'+'4'+'4'+'4'+'1'. Dice on "
"display: '22522'. The sum is: '13'='2'+'2'+'2'+'2'+'5'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '41444'. Suma je: '17'='4'+'4'+'4'+'4'+'1'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '22522'. Suma je:  '13'='2'+'2'+'2'+'2'+'5'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Full House</guilabel>: 25 points are awarded to the player if the "
"round results in three dice of a kind and a pair."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Full House</guilabel>: 25 poena je nagrađen igrač ako je rezultat "
"kruga tri kocke kao par."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dice on display: '11212'. Dice on display: '53353'."
msgstr "Prikazana kocka: '11212'. Prikazana kocka: '53353'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Small Straight</guilabel>: 30 points are awarded to the player if "
"the round results in four dice of sequential value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Small Straight</guilabel>:  Sa 30 poena je nagrađen igrač ako "
"rezultat kruga sa četiri kocke sekvencijalne vrijednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '14312'. The sequence is: '1','2','3','4'. Dice on display: "
"'51643'. The sequence is: '3','4','5','6'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '14312'. Slijed je: '1','2','3','4'. Prikazana kocka: "
"'51643'. Slijed je: '3','4','5','6'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Large Straight</guilabel>: 40 points are awarded to the player if "
"the round results in five dice of sequential value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Large Straight</guilabel>: Sa 40 poena je nagrađen igrač ako je "
"rezultat kruga sa pet kocki sekvencijalna vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '34152'. The sequence is: '1','2','3','4','5'. Dice on "
"display: '53264'. The sequence is: '2','3','4','5','6'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '34152'. Slijed je: '1','2','3','4','5'. Prikazana kocka: "
"'53264'. Slijed je: '2','3','4','5','6'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>&kiriki;</guilabel>: 50 points are awarded to the player if the "
"round results in five dice of the same value. You can score as many &kiriki; "
"as you get, for each one after the first you get an additional turn at the "
"end of the game."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>&kiriki;</guilabel>:  Sa 50 poena je nagrađen igrač ako je "
"rezultat kruga sa pet kocki iste vrijednosti. Možete osvojiti toliko "
"&kiriki; koliko dobijete, za svaki poslije prvog dobijete dodatni red na "
"kraju svake igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dice on display: '11111'. Dice on display: '33333'."
msgstr "Prikazana kocka: '11111'. Prikazana kocka: '33333'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Chance</guilabel>: Summarized value of all the dice currently on "
"display."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Chance</guilabel>:  Rezimirane vrijednosti svih kocki trenutno su "
"prikazane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dice on display: '51143'. The sum is: '14'='5'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'3'. Dice on "
"display: '21526'. The sum is: '16'='2'+'1'+'5'+'2'+'6'."
msgstr ""
"Prikazana kocka: '51143'. Suma je: '14'='5'+'1'+'1'+'4'+'3'. Prikazana "
"kocka: '21526'. Suma je: '16'='2'+'1'+'5'+'2'+'6'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Lower Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a "
#| "summary of all the fields starting from '3 of a Kind' and lower."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Lower Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a "
"summary of all the fields starting from <quote>3 of a Kind</quote> and lower."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Lower Total</guilabel>:  Polje nije za igru, samo rezime svih "
"polja od 'jedinstvenih 3' pa ispod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Grand Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a "
#| "sum of 'Upper Total' and 'Lower Total' fields."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Grand Total</guilabel>: It is not a playable field, but only a sum "
"of <quote>Upper Total</quote> and <quote>Lower Total</quote> fields."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Grand Total</guilabel>:  Polje nije za igru, samo suma 'Gornjih "
"Ukupno' i 'Donjih Ukupno' polja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other rules and constrains:"
msgstr "Druga pravila i ograničenja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The entire game round is split into 13 turns."
msgstr "Čitava igra je podijeljena u 13 okretanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each player can do one to three rolls of dice per turn."
msgstr "Svaki igrač može imati od jedan do tri bacanja koci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the first roll is done, a player can perform additional rolls for up "
"to two times (three rolls at all per turn)."
msgstr ""
"Nakon prvog bacanja, igrač moze koristiti dodatna bacanja do dva puta (tri "
"bacanja ukupno)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Player is not obligated to perform additional rolls if the first roll "
"brings satisfactory results."
msgstr ""
"Igrač nije obavezan da upotrijebi dodatna bacanja ako mu prvo bacanje donese "
"zadovoljavajuće rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each additional roll may either involve all the dice, or only the selected "
"ones."
msgstr "Svako dodatno bacanje može ili uključiti sve kocke, ili samo odabrane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A Player can select the dice to be recast by clicking on them with the mouse."
msgstr "Igrač može odabrati kocku za ponovno bacanje klikom miša na nju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the dice have been recast their previous value is lost and only the new "
"value is valid."
msgstr ""
"Jednom kad kocka bude bačena prethodne vrijednosti su izgubljene i samo nove "
"vrijednosti se računaju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result of the roll is considered satisfactory if the values of the dice "
"on display can be put into one of the score patterns discussed above."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat bacanja se računa kao zadovoljavajuci ako se vrijednost prikazane "
"kocke može staviti u jednom od obrazaca rezultata objašnjenim gore."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each individual score pattern can only be used once per game per player. "
"Therefore, once the score pattern has been used by one player it can no "
"longer be used by that same player. However, another player can still use "
"it, unless he has used this same pattern up already."
msgstr ""
"Svaki obrazac rezultata posebno može se koristiti jednom po igri po igraču. "
"Tako da, jednom kad je obrazac rezultata iskorišćen od jednog igrača ne može "
"se više koristiti od strane tog istog igrača. Kakogod, drugi igrač može "
"koristiti, osim ako več nije koristio isti obrazac."

