#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Najčešća pitanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim na promijenim izgled igre. Mogu li?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kiriki; does not currently feature any themes."
msgstr "Ne. &kiriki; trenutno ne sadrži teme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Napravio sam grešku. Mogu li poništiti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kiriki; has no <quote>Undo</quote> option."
msgstr "Ne. &kiriki; nema <quote>Undo</quote> opciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Mogu li koristiti tastaturu za igranje?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. The game of &kiriki; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. Igra &kiriki; se ne može igrati na tastaturi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne mogu da shvatim šta da radim ovdje! Ima li nagovještaja?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To learn about the game play rules and tactics please read the <link linkend="
"\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> section of this "
"handbook."
msgstr ""
"Da bi shvatili pravila igre i taktike molimo vas pročitajte  <link linkend="
"\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> odjeljak u "
"priručniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Moram napustiti igru sada, ali nisam završio još. Mogu li sačuvati svoj "
"napredak?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. There is no <quote>Save</quote> feature in &kiriki;."
msgstr "Ne. Nema <quote>Save</quote> svojstvo u &kiriki;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "The AI is too fast! I cannot see what it is doing!"
msgstr "Al je prebrz! ne mogu vidjeti šta radi!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change Artificial Intelligence's speed of action please use the game "
"configuration dialog discussed in the <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game "
"Configuration</link> section of this handbook."
msgstr ""
"Da bi promijenili brzinu umjetne inteligencije molimo vas koristite dijalog "
"konfiguracije igre koji je objašnjen u <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game "
"Configuration</link> odjeljku u priručniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:227
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Game Configuration"
msgid "<title>Game Configuration</title>"
msgstr "Konfiguracije Igre"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:235
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Game Configuration"
msgid "<phrase>Game Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "Konfiguracije Igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kiriki; configuration dialog lets you configure the number of "
"participants, manage their identities, and their response times."
msgstr ""
"&kiriki; dijalog konfiguracije dozvoljava ti da konfigurišeš broj učesnika, "
"upravljati njihovim identitetima, i njihovim vremenom odgovora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the response times for Artificial Intelligence driven players "
"only."
msgstr ""
"Možeš promijeniti vrijeme odgovora za igrače umjetne inteligencije samo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Number of players:</guilabel> this field defines the number of "
"players for &kiriki;. The values allowed here range between two and six."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> Broj igrača: </guilabel> ovo polje definiše broj igrača za "
"&kiriki;. Vrijednosti dozvoljene ovdje su između dva i šest."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>1.</guilabel>-<guilabel>6.</guilabel> Numbered fields are the "
"identities of the participating players. You can change their names as well "
"as specify whether they will be human controlled, or driven by the "
"Artificial Intelligence. To define who controls the player use a check box "
"located on the right hand side, right next to the name entry box."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>1.</guilabel>-<guilabel>6.</guilabel> Označena polja su identiteti "
"učesnika. Možete promijeniti njihova imena kao i odrediti da li će biti "
"kontrolisani od strane ljudi, ili umjetne inteligencije. Da definišete ko "
"kontroliše igrača koristite kućicu koja je locirana na desnoj strani, odmah "
"pored kutijicu za upisivanje imena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first player must always be human controlled."
msgstr "Prvi igrač mora biti kontrolisan od strane ljudi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes to number of participants and their identities will be applied on "
"the next game."
msgstr ""
"Promjene broja učesnika kao i njihovi identiteti će biti ubačeni u sljedećoj "
"igri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Delay between computers move (msec):</guilabel> lets you specify "
"the delay between Artificial Intelligence's turns. The value of this field "
"is zero by default, meaning that the Artificial Intelligence reacts "
"instantaneously."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> Kašnjenje između računarskih pokreta  (msec):</guilabel> "
"dozvoljava ti da odrediš kašnjenje reda između umjetne inteligencije. "
"Vrijednost ovog polja je nula po defaultu, što znači da Umjetna "
"inteligencija reaguje odmah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum value for this field is 999 milliseconds."
msgstr "Najveća vrijednost ovog polja je 999 milisekunde."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use <guilabel>Font Size</guilabel> and <guilabel>Row Height</guilabel> to "
#| "adjust the score board to your liking."
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Font Size:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Row Height:</guilabel> to "
"adjust the score board to your liking."
msgstr ""
"Koristi <guilabel>Font Size</guilabel> i <guilabel>Row Height</guilabel> da "
"bi odredili tablu rezultata po svom ukusu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to play immediately at &kiriki; startup disable the default "
"option <guilabel>Show demonstration game at startup</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite odmah igrati na &kiriki; pri pokretanju iskljuciti default opcije "
"<guilabel> Pokaži demonstraciju igre pri pokretanju </guilabel>."

